Billy Elliot;;89;;85;;R;;The life of 11-year-old Billy Elliot, a coal miner's son in Northern England, is forever changed one day when he stumbles upon a ballet class during his weekly boxing lesson. Before long, he finds himself in dance, demonstrating the kind of raw talent seldom seen by the class' exacting instructor, Mrs. Wilkinson. With a tart tongue and a never-ending stream of cigarettes in her hand, Mrs. Wilkinson's zest for teaching is revived when she sees Billy's potential.;;Drama,Lgbtq+;;Stephen Daldry;;2000;;Julie Walters,Jamie Bell,Jamie Draven,Gary Lewis,Jean Heywood,Stuart Wells,Nicola Blackwell,Adam Cooper,Mike Elliot;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/billy_elliot